&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Cyber and Technology E&amp;amp;O insurance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Existing relationships with potential broker partners&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical background in cybersecurity, engineering, or computer science is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
