&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a remote position that can be based anywhere in Australia.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
