&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience adjusting cyber claims&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Law Degree or Bachelors Degree is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience in working as part of a team, interacting with others, meeting goals, and successfully performing in a changing work environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and interactive skills&lt;/li&gt;
