&lt;li&gt;Maintain audit-ready processes, documentation, and evidence to support internal and external reviews.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Claims, Actuarial, Data, Product, and Engineering on strategic initiatives and operational roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
