&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;About us&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Coalition is the world&#39;s first Active Insurance provider designed to help prevent digital risk before it strikes. Founded in 2017, Coalition combines comprehensive insurance coverage and innovative cybersecurity tools to help businesses manage and mitigate potential cyberattacks.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Opportunities to make an impact with bold thinking are real—and happening daily at Coalition.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Coalition is seeking an experienced, relationship-oriented professional to join our team as a &lt;strong&gt;Client Executive&lt;/strong&gt; supporting clients and partners across Germany and the European market.&lt;/p&gt;
In this role, you will build and strengthen long-term relationships with strategic clients and brokers, helping organizations realize the full value of Coalition’s cyber insurance and security capabilities. You will work closely with senior stakeholders to understand business priorities, provide strategic guidance, and ensure a high-quality client experience. The ideal candidate brings significant experience in account management and client engagement within commercial insurance, strong executive presence, and the ability to engage credibly with senior stakeholders across complex organizations.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Working closely with Allianz and key account managers&lt;/strong&gt;, you will also help identify opportunities to expand Coalition’s cyber solutions within Allianz’s client portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is a full time, remote-first position, that can be based anywhere in Germany.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage strategic client relationships across Germany and Europe, with a focus on long-term partnership, retention, and growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop trusted relationships with senior stakeholders, including Risk Managers, CISOs, CTOs, brokers, and executive decision-makers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a trusted advisor by understanding client priorities and aligning Coalition’s solutions to their business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead stewardship and account review meetings, providing insights, performance updates, and strategic recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
