&lt;li&gt;Develop, oversee, and enhance actuarial models, setting methodology standards and driving continuous improvement through dedicated project work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex analytical findings into clear recommendations for internal and external audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SME to support the creation and maintenance of appropriate pricing risk governance controls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Straddle the worlds of reinsurance, data science, engineering and security experts to shape the most suitable data-driven solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as an ambassador for the actuarial team, fostering a solutions-driven approach and demonstrating a strong commitment in meeting the needs of our stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
